This paper discusses learning an Optimal Map using neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions applications in computer vision (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY), which are common areas of research in machine learning. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of dynamic flows, which is a technique commonly used in neural network optimization (cs.NE).
